            "formula": "",
            "calculated_format": "",
            "blank_if_zero": 0,
            "readonly": 0,
            "message": "1. Working space and access to a telephone, internet and photocopying facilities\r\n2. Knowledgeable person to accompany during the audit.\r\n3. Knowledgeable person to handle the selected technology, to present the data/information\r\n4. Access to pertinent manuals, procedures and to access the required data/information\r\n5. Safety Requirements as per your procedures\r\n6. Should you have any query with regard to the arrangements for this audit, please contact us.\"",
